Product IDE:
    - Olympus Workspace for each Foundry Workshop (multiple workspaces per workshop)
    - Olympus Rocket (IDE) for each Foundry Workshop
    - Workshop -> Workspace -> Rocket (IDE)
    - Editing content across all the foundry repositories
    - Foundry Workshops for Tenants
    - Workshop is a Olympus Hub Workbench as well
    - Workshop has Rocke profile that determines the default IDE Plugins, Views, and Settings
